definitions.definition: A member of the crew of a spaceship or other spacecraft that travels beyond Earth's atmosphere, or someone trained to serve that purpose.

subdefinitions.definition: An American space traveler, when contrasted against equivalent terms from other countries such as cosmonaut , taikonaut , spationaut , and vyomanaut .

definitions.definition: A person (typically man) working abroad away from their family .

main_definition: A member of the crew of a spaceship or other spacecraft that travels beyond Earth's atmosphere, or someone trained to serve that purpose.
secondary_definitions: ( Hong Kong ) A person (typically man) working abroad away from their family .
